nanoc
ruby

runs on your local computer and compiles documents written in formats 
such as Markdown, Textile, Hamlâ€¦ into a static web site consisting of 
simple HTML files, ready for uploading to any web server

1. gem install nanoc
2. gem install kramdown
3. gem install adsf

4. nanoc create_site tutorial

5. cd tutorial
   nanoc compile
   
6. nanoc view
   this will start web server
   
7. http://localhost:3000/

